<!-- History Section -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our History</h2>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-orange-400 mx-auto"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Education is the process of imparting or acquiring knowledge, values, and skills that, ideally, contribute to improving learners and society. However, the goals and methods of education vary considerably between cultures and religions. This distinction is seen in how education is practiced in Islamic and Western societies.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Islamic education centres on teaching Islam and its religious way of life. The source of Islamic education is the Qur'an, the central religious text of Islam. What does the Qur'an teach? The Qur'an imparts to Muslims the core beliefs of Islam and the teachings of the Prophet Muhammad. For Muslim education, the Qur'an is the sacred writings of the Prophet Muhammad revealed to him by the Archangel Gabriel. Muslims regard the Prophet's revelations in the Qur'an as sacred, representing the word of God. Consequently, education in Islam and its teachings are paramount in a young person's development.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Governing Board Section -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Governing Board Members</h2>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-orange-400 mx-auto"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Chairman Profile -->
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
            <div class="bg-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-start gap-8">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <img src="~/images/about_us/chairman_dr_ehsanul_haque.jpg" alt="Dr Ehsanul Haque" class="w-32 h-32 lg:w-40 lg:h-40 rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-orange-400">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 text-center lg:text-left">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Dr Ehsanul Haque</h3>
                        <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Chairman</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                            Dr Ehsanul Haque graduated from BUET and joined the Department of Materials and Metallurgical Engineering as a Lecturer. He in time became a Professor, Head of the Department, and Dean of Engineering at BUET. He did his Masters from the University of Sheffield and PhD from the University of Birmingham in the UK. He was a member of the board of trustees of Ahsanullah University of Science and Technology, Dhaka. He was the first Vice Chancellor of KUET and served as a member of the University Grants Commission of Bangladesh. He is now involved with the Bangladesh Ethics Foundation for the propagation of ethical values.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Other Board Members -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Principal -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/160?img=20" alt="Suraiya Khan" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover border-4 border-orange-400">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Suraiya Khan</h3>
                <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold">Principal</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Vice Principal -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <img src="~/images/about_us/samia_yousuf.jpg" alt="Samia Yousuf" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover border-4 border-orange-400">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Samia Yousuf</h3>
                <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold">Vice Principal</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Independent Director -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/160?img=22" alt="Nasir Ahmed" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover border-4 border-orange-400">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Nasir Ahmed</h3>
                <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold">Independent Director</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Director & COO -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <img src="~/images/about_us/nafis_ahmed.jpg" alt="Nafis Ahmed" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover border-4 border-orange-400">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Nafis Ahmed</h3>
                <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold">Director & COO</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Manager -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <img src="~/images/about_us/md_mohibbul_islam.jpg" alt="Md. Mohibbul Islam" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover border-4 border-orange-400">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Md. Mohibbul Islam</h3>
                <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold">Manager (Accounts & IT)</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>